<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Viewing Metrics Data</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>The user interface for monitoring your services and virtual machines integrates with Grafana, an open-source application for visualizing large-scale metrics data. <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> ships with a preconfigured dashboard that visualizes the monitoring data collected from your services and virtual machines. </p>
            <p>To access the dashboard, use the <uicontrol>Grafana Home</uicontrol> option located along the top of the <uicontrol>Overview</uicontrol> page.</p>
